{
 "name": "RPlog_Prison_Visitations",
 "title": "Prison Visitations",
 "summary": "Imprisoned aboard a ship in cells of steel and wire, the eccentric Mira and the drugged, captured dark adept Simon Sezirok are visited by the tormented dark Jedi Cort -- also called Etrigan -- and the deadly hunter Kacela, the 'Butcher,' who helped capture them. Cort, who sees much of himself in Simon, uses his gifts to slip past the sentries and brings Mira to Simon's cell, while the scarred Morganna looks on with condescending menace. As Simon realizes the Imperials may intend to torture Mira to break him, he warily confronts Cort and Kacela about their allegiance to the Corrupter. The tense visitation leaves the prisoners' fates hanging in the balance.",
